reclassify the Construction in Progress - Infrastructure Asset of P11,841,215 to Road Net Work account;
close the Due to NGAs account of P11,866,215.80 in the Trust Fund and;
transfer the Road Network  account to the General Fund and record the corresponding Government Equity account   in order to reflect the correct balances of the accounts affected, and;
Management return the unexpended/excess funds of P2,163,784.20 to the National Treasury.

